# XS650 Safety Relay Replacement (1980–1983 Yamaha XS650)

## Professional Dual-Relay Replacement Solution

---

# Overview

This project recreates the factory Yamaha XS650 Safety Relay using modern, easily available automotive components.

The original Yamaha unit performed two important jobs:

1. Disabled the starter motor after the engine started
2. Delayed the headlight turning on until the engine was running

Unfortunately, original safety relay modules are now:
- expensive
- unreliable
- difficult to source
- commonly failed internally due to age

This project replaces the factory module using:

- 2 × standard automotive relays
- 1 × resistor
- 1 × diode

No microcontrollers.
No programming.
No exotic parts.

The system behaves almost identically to the original Yamaha design.

